Who bears burden?	State must justify each stage	Claimant must show decision was beyond the range of rationality
Variable intensity?	Yes — MWRF in welfare/resource cases (SC); full proportionality in rights cases (Tigere majority)	Yes — 'anxious scrutiny' in fundamental rights cases (ex p Smith)
Merits substitution risk?	Higher — court asks if less restrictive means existed	Lower — court only asks if decision was within a reasonable range
